{"tid":1458894,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"正面衝突戰術開始不利 係咪要轉攻擊香港經濟？","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:02:40.000Z","uid":267399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e21352add4b8f8c2c578756d17a0c40eeb6b3eb7","tid":1458894,"uid":267399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"分享個人睇法   只求討論 <br />\n<br />\n好簡單咁諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗方軍力不停升級  催淚彈&gt;白衣勢力&gt;過期彈&gt;槍&gt;槍射頭&gt;福建佬&gt;水炮車<br />\n同時d狗犯灑規都唔洗負責<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反我方<br />\n連登成日有post話要行動升級  又升唔到  又怕太暴力<br />\n受傷人數  被捕人數  只係越多  每次傷勢越嚴重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加正面抗爭開始對我地劣勢  所以我咁諗<br />\n<br />\n衝突只係引起社會注意 只係抗爭ga前菜  我覺得2個月都已經令好多中立同淺藍都變支持我地   支持人數已經開始飽和 d深藍都已經冇得遊說<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該改變戰術  靠人數 集中係經濟方面攻擊 好似上次罷工咁<br />\n用經濟威脅政府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\np.s: p牌仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由反送中先開ac 希望各位巴打唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b972fac1c6f340917e7d110beab14204de71c32c","tid":1458894,"uid":267399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"推  只求討論"},{"pid":"d10d293f5f5813473134912caa5e11fecb48c6dc","tid":1458894,"uid":267399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"巴打們點睇？<br />\nd狗越黎越冇底線"},{"pid":"3b111af8cc64377e2958289a1f4d652be823ee11","tid":1458894,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"係要咁做<br />\n但未諗到點樣唔影響民心但又夠力既方案"},{"pid":"6612b8dd7eb20e57f1127ca81680ecd16f01e752","tid":1458894,"uid":267399,"like":0,"dislike